{"title":"Shell编程：基本运算符和流程控制","uid":"265b24ec3639f60cad27203b44d3a6f9","slug":"Linux-Shell03","date":"2020-04-13T08:11:51.000Z","updated":"2020-05-08T01:42:30.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Linux-Shell03.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<h1 id=\"基本运算符\"><a href=\"#基本运算符\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"基本运算符\"></a>基本运算符</h1><h2 id=\"算术运算符\"><a href=\"#算术运算符\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"算术运算符\"></a>算术运算符</h2><ul>\n<li>和其他编程语言差不多<br><img src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200413161602.png\" alt=\"算术运算符\"><span id=\"more\"></span></li>\n<li>使用<code>$(())</code>对整数进行数值计算<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">a&#x3D;10\nb&#x3D;20\nval&#x3D;$((a+b))\necho &quot;a + b : $val&quot;</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"关系运算符\"><a href=\"#关系运算符\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"关系运算符\"></a>关系运算符</h2><img src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200413163401.png\" alt=\"关系运算符\"></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"布尔运算符\"><a href=\"#布尔运算符\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"布尔运算符\"></a>布尔运算符</h2><p><img src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200413170753.png\" alt=\"布尔运算符\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"逻辑运算符\"><a href=\"#逻辑运算符\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"逻辑运算符\"></a>逻辑运算符</h2><p><img src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200413170829.png\" alt=\"逻辑运算符\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"字符串运算符\"><a href=\"#字符串运算符\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"字符串运算符\"></a>字符串运算符</h2><p><img src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200413170907.png\" alt=\"字符串运算符\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"文件测试运算符\"><a href=\"#文件测试运算符\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"文件测试运算符\"></a>文件测试运算符</h2><p><img src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200413170951.png\" alt=\"文件测试运算符\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"流程控制\"><a href=\"#流程控制\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"流程控制\"></a>流程控制</h1><h2 id=\"if判断\"><a href=\"#if判断\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"if判断\"></a>if判断</h2><ul>\n<li>语法格式:<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">if condition1\nthen\n    command1\nelif condition2 \nthen \n    command2\nelse\n    commandN\nfi</code></pre></li>\n<li>举例<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">#!&#x2F;bin&#x2F;bash\nread grade\nif (( $grade &gt;&#x3D; 90 ))\nthen\n    echo &quot;优秀&quot;\nelif (( $grade &gt;&#x3D; 80 ))\nthen\n    echo &quot;良&quot;\nelif (( $grade &gt;&#x3D; 60  ))\nthen\n    echo &quot;及格&quot;\nelse\n    echo &quot;不及格&quot;\nfi</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"for-循环\"><a href=\"#for-循环\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"for 循环\"></a>for 循环</h2></li>\n<li>语法格式：<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">for var in item1 item2 ... itemN\ndo\n    command1\n    command2\n    ...\n    commandN\ndone</code></pre>\n或者<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">for ((;;))\ndo \n    command1\n    command2\n    ...\n    commandN\ndone\n</code></pre></li>\n<li>举例<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">for loop in 1 2 3 4 5\ndo\n    echo &quot;The value is: $loop&quot;\ndone</code></pre>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">for str in &#39;This is a string&#39;\ndo\n    echo $str\ndone</code></pre>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">sum&#x3D;0\nfor((i&#x3D;1;i&lt;10;i++))\ndo \n    ((sum+&#x3D;i))\ndone\necho &quot;$sum&quot;</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"while-语句\"><a href=\"#while-语句\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"while 语句\"></a>while 语句</h2></li>\n<li>语法格式<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">while condition\ndo\n    command\ndone</code></pre></li>\n<li>举例<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">int&#x3D;1\nwhile(( $int&lt;&#x3D;5 ))\ndo\n    echo $int\n    let &quot;int++&quot;\ndone</code></pre></li>\n</ul>\n","text":"基本运算符算术运算符 和其他编程语言差不多 使用$(())对整数进行数值计算a&#x3D;10 b&#x3D;20 val&#x3D;$((a+b)) echo &quot;a + b : $val&quot; 关系运算符 布尔运算符 逻辑运算符 字符串运算符 文件测试运算符 流...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Linux","slug":"Linux","count":4,"path":"api/categories/Linux.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Linux","slug":"Linux","count":4,"path":"api/tags/Linux.json"},{"name":"Shell","slug":"Shell","count":3,"path":"api/tags/Shell.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E8%BF%90%E7%AE%97%E7%AC%A6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">基本运算符</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%AF%E8%BF%90%E7%AE%97%E7%AC%A6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">算术运算符</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E8%BF%90%E7%AE%97%E7%AC%A6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">关系运算符</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%B8%83%E5%B0%94%E8%BF%90%E7%AE%97%E7%AC%A6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">布尔运算符</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91%E8%BF%90%E7%AE%97%E7%AC%A6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">逻辑运算符</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E4%B8%B2%E8%BF%90%E7%AE%97%E7%AC%A6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">字符串运算符</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95%E8%BF%90%E7%AE%97%E7%AC%A6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">文件测试运算符</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">流程控制</span></a><ol class=\